Package: maicChecks
Type: Package
Title: Assessing the Numerical Feasibility for Conducting a Matching-Adjusted Indirect Comparison (MAIC)
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2024-06-06
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Lillian", "Yau", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maicChecks@gmail.com"), 
